item.title: CVE-2023-32325|2024-08-02T15:10:24.912Z -- posthog -- posthog-js
item.description: PostHog-js is a library to interface with the PostHog analytics tool. Versions prior to 1.57.2 have the potential for cross-site scripting. Problem has been patched in 1.57.2. Users are advised to upgrade. Users unable to upgrade should ensure that their Content Security Policy is in place.
